{"tid":1719500,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"尖沙咀真係好撚廢","createTime":"2019-11-14T06:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T23:27:52.000Z","uid":176834,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad2214808598cd7ef3a9f31f2a7ab94823c084a","tid":1719500,"uid":176834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"唔好叫和你lunch喇 叫和你撚啦<br />\n連續撚咗手足兩次<br />\n星期二又話有行動推撚咗幾十版<br />\n中午出到去完全冇人<br />\n4點話要快閃 之後咩事都冇發生<br />\n到6點先有一個手足掟咗一下玻璃 跟住就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日又話要開花推撚咗差唔多廿版<br />\n出到嚟廿個都冇<br />\n其他區中午求其吹下雞都幾百人<br />\n尖沙咀推到廿鳩幾版都冇人<br />\n真係好撚柒廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔會再對尖沙咀人抱有任何期望"},{"pid":"53741a8dd9c488e66ac887733facf309ad9a219c","tid":1719500,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5022bf5bd9f195f0a0a62c5eb18b27b79bc4111","tid":1719500,"uid":284451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ad2214808598cd7ef3a9f31f2a7ab94823c084a","tid":1719500,"uid":176834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"唔好叫和你lunch喇 叫和你撚啦<br />\n連續撚咗手足兩次<br />\n星期二又話有行動推撚咗幾十版<br />\n中午出到去完全冇人<br />\n4點話要快閃 之後咩事都冇發生<br />\n到6點先有一個手足掟咗一下玻璃 跟住就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日又話要開花推撚咗差唔多廿版<br />\n出到嚟廿個都冇<br />\n其他區中午求其吹下雞都幾百人<br />\n尖沙咀推到廿鳩幾版都冇人<br />\n真係好撚柒廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔會再對尖沙咀人抱有任何期望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"和你撚  +1"},{"pid":"13e1ebc51ed5f5f3773e7fa336001af7980661cc","tid":1719500,"uid":106121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"走咗啦，我由12 點幾開始由海港城行去每一個集合點都唔見人.. 最後喺碼頭食咗半個鐘風"},{"pid":"95dba7bae1ba40dd1d6bd624d9097815e9d10bb8","tid":1719500,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618fcdf3cead84e8b95a285ef2926a8eb567fc67","tid":1719500,"uid":191090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀次次都係咁，<br />\n除非你其他地方集合再入尖咀就會多人嚕，<br />\n除左之前梳士巴利花園個次未見過有人。"},{"pid":"8fe5846521ddfd8a0028bba88d1d55cfbd5e21bf","tid":1719500,"uid":121783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"130左右去咗廣東道,碼頭都唔見人聚集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac76062ebbe9f4bb7671f30d0e2c4729964bcd0","tid":1719500,"uid":166695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe5846521ddfd8a0028bba88d1d55cfbd5e21bf","tid":1719500,"uid":121783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"130左右去咗廣東道,碼頭都唔見人聚集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n不知所謂！吾黎就吾好吹雞啦"},{"pid":"7bb90f201c0ac722e471a0088563453aa5391da7","tid":1719500,"uid":24838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"真心...喺度返工都灰爆 lunch吹極雞都係咁少人"},{"pid":"9153e7ba0804d63e2932140b89233191dc7fe135","tid":1719500,"uid":75449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"唉好失望"},{"p